## Extending this rubric library

See `skills/hd-review/assets/starter-rubrics/skill-quality.md § Extending this rubric` for the pattern to author a new rubric. When a rubric criterion recurs across lessons in `docs/knowledge/`, consider promoting it via `/hd:maintain rule-propose`.

## How rubrics are applied

```
Task design-harnessing:review:rubric-applicator(
  work_item_path: "<path to PR diff, component, or screen>",
  rubric_path: "docs/rubrics/<rubric-name>.md"
)
```

Or interactively: `/hd:review critique <path>` — the skill picks matching rubrics from this INDEX.

